README for HoopAThon Website

## HoopAThon Event Page

This repository contains a static non-profit event page for HoopAThon, an annual
fundraiser held in April.

### Included functionality

- Event overview and mission details
- "How pledges work" section (per-basket and lump sum)
- Donation link to Prince George Community Foundation Flow Through Fund
- Individual participant signup form
- Corporate team signup form
- Community impact tracker (individual and team signup counts)
- Corporate sponsorship tiers with contact info

Form signups are stored in Supabase. 
